<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> samadhigatapaṁcamahāśa<note n="257-2">The continuation is lost.</note>
<lb n="2"/><unclear>sva</unclear>sti sakavaruṣaṁbulu 1157 gu nēṁṭṭi viṣu
<lb n="3" break="no"/>vusaṁkrāṁttikālamunaśrīmanmahā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>maṁḍalēśvara kōnakaṁḍravāḍi sū
<lb n="5" break="no"/>rapōtarājulu bejavāḍa mallēśva
<lb n="6" break="no"/>raśrīmahādēvaraku Akhaṁḍadīpā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>laku drubbupolamunaṁdu rēṁgula
<lb n="8" break="no"/>cēnu puṭyaṁḍu niddumunu mōca
<lb n="9" break="no"/>pāṭidakṣiṇāna nenamaṁdumunu
<lb n="10" break="no"/>kā <unclear>be</unclear>rasi bhūmi dīpānaku nicina
<lb n="11"/>kha 1 na 10 <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> marini sūrapōtarājuṁ
<lb n="12" break="no"/>gārē Ī viṣuvusaṁkrāṁttikālamunaṁ
<lb n="13" break="no"/>da bejavāḍa mallīśvaraśrīmahādēvaraku
<lb n="14"/>Akhaṁḍadīpanaku Iccina InpaEḍlu 55 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
<lb n="15"/>vīniṁ jēkoni dēvānabhōyinikoḍku
<lb n="16"/>mallebhōyuṁḍu muppanabhō
<lb n="17" break="no"/>yuṁḍunu pōtanabhōyuṁḍu<unclear>nu</unclear>
<lb n="18"/>kamanābhōyuṁḍu tama putrā
<lb n="19" break="no"/>nupautrikamuna Ācaṁdrārkkamugānu
<lb n="20"/>nitye Aḍḍeṁḍu neyi pōyaṁgala
<lb n="21" break="no"/>varu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Ā bhōlaku darbhaṟēmapaḍu
<lb n="22" break="no"/>maṭa bhūmi kha 1 <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> svadaṁttapara
<lb n="23" break="no"/>dattaṁ va Ō harēti vasuṁddharā[ṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>*] ṣaṣṭiva
<lb n="24" break="no"/><supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>ṣasahasraṇi viṣṭhayā<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied> jāyatē krimi[ḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>*]
